entry.title: New release for Obtainium: v1.1.6
entry.content:
What's Changed

  • Fix some questions of 简体中文（Simplified Chinese） and English. by @ArcticFoxPro in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1562
  • Use applicationId for provider authorities by @jmoerschbach in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1560
  • Spanish update by @CertainBot in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1559
  • Fixes by @re7gog in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1556
  • Update de.json by @DwainZwerg in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1555
  • By @ImranR98 in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1567:
  • Share apps.obtainium.imranr.dev config links instead of HTML raw (#1553)
  • Remove foreground requirement for Shizuku (#1561)
  • Fix "illegal encoding" error (#1563)

New Contributors

  • @ArcticFoxPro made their first contribution in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1562
  • @jmoerschbach made their first contribution in https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/pull/1560

Full Changelog: https://github.com/ImranR98/Obtainium/compare/v1.1.5...v1.1.6
